Description: GMB should be Successful from USSD
GMB should be Successful from USSD when subscriber who is not Registered is doing GMB
GMB should not be Successful from USSD when Maximum Daily Limit Reached
GMB should not be Successful from USSD when Maximum Weekly Limit Reached
GMB should not be Successful from USSD when Monthly  Limit Reached
GMB should not be Successful from USSD when Maximum daily Amount Reached
GMB should not be Successful from USSD when Weekly  Amount reached
GMB should not be Successful from USSD when maximum Monthly Amount reached
GMB should Not be Successful from USSD When we do not enter Mandatory parameters
GMB should Not be Successful from USSD When MSISDN1 Length is not Between Specified SystemPreference MIN_MSISDN_LENGTH and MAX_MSISDN_LENGTH
GMB should Not be Successful from USSD When MSISDN2 Length is not Between Specified SystemPreference MIN_MSISDN_LENGTH and MAX_MSISDN_LENGTH
